; Regression test for issue #2005: --permissive with balance assignments.
;
; When a posting uses balance assignment syntax with no explicit amount
; (e.g., Assets:Checking =$12345) and the assigned amount would cause
; the transaction not to balance, --permissive should accept the
; transaction by reverting to auto-balancing (computing the amount
; needed to balance the other postings).

2021/02/14 Test transaction
  Liabilities:Visa  $3141
  Assets:Checking  =$12345

test bal --permissive
              $-3141  Assets:Checking
               $3141  Liabilities:Visa
--------------------
                   0
end test

; Without --permissive, the same transaction should still error.
test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 11:
While balancing transaction from "$FILE", lines 9-11:
> 2021/02/14 Test transaction
>   Liabilities:Visa  $3141
>   Assets:Checking  =$12345
Unbalanced remainder is:
              $15486
Amount to balance against:
              $15486
Error: Transaction does not balance
end test
